Solved: increase the hardware serial port baud rate to 115200 in line 142 of 'main':<div class="codebox"><p>CODE: </p><pre><code>//Serial.begin(9600);Serial.begin(115200);</code></pre></div>Then you can see debug messages via USB like this:<div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="http://skysedge.us/forum/download/file.php?id=12" class="postimage" alt="monitor.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://skysedge.us/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1724">SteveC</a> — Sun Apr 26, 2020 4:04 pm</p><hr />
